. "Let ${ \/}$ be the transition matrix for an ergodic chain. 
   Let ${ \/}_n$ be the matrix defined by $$ { \/}_n = \frac{{ 
   \/} + { \/} + { \/}^2 +\cdots + { \/}^n}{n + 1}\ . $$ Then 
   ${ \/}_n \to { \/}$, where ${ \/}$ is a matrix all of whose 
   rows are equal to the unique fixed probability vector ${ 
   \/}$ for ${ \/}$."
